Subject: reject alg=none in view-token verifier

verifyView dispatches by the alg field on the JOSE header and the "none"
branch accepts the token when the signature segment is empty. A forged
token with admin-ish claims passes the scope check and the handler
returns the brief body. Allow only HS256.

